                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601362840469-51e4d8d58785?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Detailing Ergebnis" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition duration-700" loading="lazy" width="400" height="400" />
